{"tid":1387340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(震驚60億人) 救班義士嘅方法只有一個","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T14:02:39.000Z","uid":67303,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"761bec24168af765c77bf1cba1ecd96df47d6400","tid":1387340,"uid":67303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:41:47.000Z","msg":"就係令到場運動成功<br />\n<br />\n71係立法會入面果位義士講得好岩 我地今次再輸 就會輸10年 甚至係永不翻生<br />\n<br />\n除左自6月以黎俾人拉左嘅義士要受牢獄之苦外 仲會有無數人會被清算 包括所有係呢場運動內以不同形式表達過反政府嘅人 不論勇武派 和理非 媒體 連登... 而幸存嘅人永遠都會活係白色恐怖之下 以後再唔會有抗爭出現<br />\n<br />\n所以呢場運動真係香港人嘅最後一戰 為左被捕嘅義士 為左香港 為左我地嘅下一代 我地一定要贏<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b3cbe7a017be08a2cb95fba43903ff52418cc0ce","tid":1387340,"uid":141827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:42:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"98226ed5a478664da3219ba445435b90c0bb4159","tid":1387340,"uid":67303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c2b430338f91c38f3f21e336546dfbf0e3c8e891","tid":1387340,"uid":67303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:54:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f14b549a0587fc37fe740db1c098b544d35fb88","tid":1387340,"uid":67303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb005253f56aac0f5646c651f6ad50ceb6c16847","tid":1387340,"uid":67303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:02:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}